3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:04,840
What are you doing here?

4
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:05,879
Go, quickly.

5
00:01:06,159 --> 00:01:07,000
I'm not leaving.

6
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,760
Foolish human.

7
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,439
You can't bear this.

8
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:18,840
Go!

9
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,439
Return the Chi pearl to your body now,

10
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,879
or you'll die.

11
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:28,879
I no longer have the power
to draw the Mei pearl back into me.

12
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:32,239
I've always hated letting others
see me in a pathetic state.

13
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:33,920
