14
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,000
I told you,

15
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:41,079
I'll stay by your side.

16
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:46,239
(Jing Haisi,)

17
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,799
(don't forget me.)

18
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:57,599
(I'll use the little power I have left,)

19
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,640
(to return the Chi pearl to your body.)

20
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:03,000
(Jing Haisi,)

21
