23
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,479
(I regret it.)

24
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,280
What's her name?

25
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,039
She's a dancer from Shanghai.

26
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,080
Her name is Gu Meng.

27
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:26,840
Gu Meng!

28
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,039
Your perfume

29
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,479
smells awful.

30
00:02:57,479 --> 00:02:58,319
What are you doing here?

31
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:00,879
You're not the only one

32
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:01,919
who cares about Wujian.

33
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,240
Li Motong.

34
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:08,120
Thank you.

35
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:09,840
If you have time to talk nonsense,

36
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,240
use it to repair the cracks
in Wujian instead.

37
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:34,599
What I owed you,

38
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,120
I've returned it.

39
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:55,560
Are you alright?

40
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:56,560
Jing Haisi.

41
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:02,319
All these years I've been against you,

42
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:06,560
because I knew
she was your fated calamity of love.

43
00:04:07,639 --> 00:04:09,199
I only wanted you to live.

44
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,800
But I still couldn't change your fate.

45
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:20,160
The Mei pearl
has now merged with her body.

46
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,240
If Wujian is to be saved,

47
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,519
