have a future?

90
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,519
But you're

91
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:40,560
a handsome flower.

92
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,319
The magnolia's meaning is

93
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,199
pure and sincere love.

94
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,560
When the magnolia blooms,

95
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,160
my eyes are full of you.

96
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:54,240
I want to hold you like this

97
00:06:54,759 --> 00:06:55,920
through every meal and every season.

98
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,639
To have you every day

99
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,439
for a lifetime.

100
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,639
Nothing in this world

101
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:03,959
can ever separate us.

102
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,120
Not even death.

103
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,079
