must also protect her king.

107
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,519
Let go!

108
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:20,600
I said I won't!

109
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:22,439
Lu Huayan,

110
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:25,439
Will you be my one and only bride,

111
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,759
destined for me through

112
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,560
all lifetimes?

113
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,759
I am willing.

